-- Mesa Air Says Unsecured Creditors Can File Reorganization Plan in January
-- B y   D o n a l d   J e f f r e y
-- 2010-10-12T13:37:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/mesa-air-says-unsecured-creditors-can-file-reorganization-plan-in-january.html
Mesa Air Group Inc., the bankrupt
regional airline, agreed to let creditors with unsecured claims
file their own reorganization plan in January, if the company’s
own plan hasn’t been approved yet, according to court papers
filed yesterday in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donald Jeffrey in New York at 
